text = "A grading system has stopped  
working, and three student scores  
need to be checked.  

The scores are [color=#2FA084]90[/color], [color=#2FA084]71[/color], and [color=#2FA084]75[/color].  

The passing score is [color=#2FA084]75[/color],  
so any score that is [color=#2FA084]75[/color] or higher  
should be marked as [color=#2FA084]PASS[/color] and  
score that is lower [color=#2FA084]74[/color] is [color=#2FA084]FAIL[/color]."

